Body:
Description: I was looking for data from an AD report regarding Weak PWs, when I found an error:
'AD/daily/user/AD_weakpasswords "Job connection profile is not available"'

@Mike Candon​ The most likely cause for this is the job connection profile is not set at the job level which is a requirement for that specific job.
